---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="reviews">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        What creators are saying about Storys.ai
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join thousands of storytellers who are already creating amazing visual novels with AI
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Sarah Chen</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Visual Novel Creator</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"Storys.ai completely transformed how I create visual novels. The AI character generation is incredible - I can create complex personalities in minutes instead of hours. My readers love the depth and consistency of my characters now!"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-1.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Marcus Rodriguez</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Game Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"The 2D/3D environment tools are game-changing! I can prototype entire worlds in a fraction of the time. The AI suggestions for world-building elements are spot-on and really help with creative blocks."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Emma Thompson</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Interactive Fiction Writer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"Interactive storytelling has never been easier! The branching narrative tools let me create complex storylines that readers can truly influence. My audience engagement has increased dramatically since switching to Storys.ai."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-3.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Alex Kim</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Indie Game Studio Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"As a small indie studio, Storys.ai has been a lifesaver. We can focus on creative direction while AI handles the technical heavy lifting. Our production time has been cut in half!"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-4.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">David Park</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Digital Artist</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"The community features are amazing! I've connected with other creators, shared ideas, and even collaborated on projects. The feedback system has helped me improve my storytelling skills dramatically."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Lisa Wang</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Creative Director</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">"Storys.ai has democratized visual novel creation. Even with no technical background, I can create professional-quality stories. The AI suggestions are incredibly intuitive and always enhance my creative vision."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>